  "title": "How to set up at ServiceAccount with a Discovery Management role",
  "slug": "serviceaccount",
  "categorySlug": "data-sources",
  "html": "<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section kb-article-row-0-padding\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-2\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h1 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">How to set up at ServiceAccount with a Discovery Management role</h1>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">To automatically scann all users in Exchange, you must create a Service Account with the Discovery Management role.</h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\">Go the Exchange admin centre (EAC) to add Discovery Management role to <a href=\"mailto:gdprscan@yourorganisation.xxx\">gdprscan@yourorganisation.xxx</a>.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"199\" style=\"width: 624px;\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/HllgprpyJlpd5Ib9nxbf7YHbgIWm1zpLhgH6Go4uJnjjWopniITUWyDDY4F-8nTtq9WQ6ypSNLvjVSkLg2d7Ga9TJzoK_MpOPZuO__9F04uIXt8Gi5wRtenduMDczxnMC7sHY9He\" width=\"624\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hubfs/image-png-4.png\"></p>\n<div class=\"hs-callout-type-tip\" data-hs-callout-type=\"tip\">\n<p>Make sure that the Service Account have a valid email address</p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>For more information on how to add the Discovery Management role see:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/Exchange/policy-and-compliance/ediscovery/assign-permissions?redirectedfrom=MSDN&amp;view=exchserver-2019\">https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/Exchange/policy-and-compliance/ediscovery/assign-permissions?redirectedfrom=MSDN&amp;view=exchserver-2019</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"hs-callout-type-warning\" data-hs-callout-type=\"warning\">\n<p>Make sure you are using providing the PRIMARY SMTP address for the service account to data &amp; more.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Go to&nbsp;</p>\n<p>admin.exchange.microsoft.com</p>\n<p>Mailboxes</p>\n<p>search for the service account and check the mail address</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hubfs/image-png-Jun-22-2021-09-18-37-68-AM.png\"></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
  "sourceUrl": "https://support.dataandmore.com/en/knowledge/serviceaccount"
}